      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget Buy Alert \u2013 Honest Deal for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\udd27\n\nLooking for the most affordable way to get on the road? Let's be straight with you: this vehicle is in poor condition. It has visible wear, mechanical issues that will need attention, and is best suited for someone who is handy with repairs or looking for a project car. That said, it runs and could be a great opportunity for the right person willing to put in some work! Perfect for a budget-conscious buyer, a first-time driver, or someone who loves a good fixer-upper. Come take a look and see if this one fits your needs!",
