    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly mint condition \u2014 and we mean that sincerely. The exterior is virtually flawless, with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections to speak of. The paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine, and all body panels are perfectly aligned. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery, dashboard, and all surfaces are spotless, showing no signs of wear, fading, or damage. Every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly with no unusual noises or issues. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission \u2014 are in top working order. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely feels and drives like new. Ideal for a buyer who wants the reliability and feel of a new car at a used-car price.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we are genuinely proud to present what is arguably one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint gleams with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Body panel alignment is precise, all trim pieces are intact and pristine, and the glass is crystal clear without chips or cracks. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface is clean and unmarked. All electronics, controls, and convenience features function perfectly, including climate control, infotainment, power accessories, and safety systems. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, starting immediately and running with a smooth, confident purr. Service history is current and complete. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and truly shows it \u2014 a buyer who demands the best will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A fantastic opportunity for the budget-savvy buyer seeking reliable everyday transportation! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it has some visible wear and minor cosmetic imperfections that reflect its history on the road, but it runs and gets you where you need to go. The mechanical fundamentals are intact, making this a practical choice for someone who values function over flash. If you're looking for affordable, dependable wheels without the premium price tag, this one deserves a look!",
