    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a mint-condition car, representing the very best the used market has to offer. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint gleams with a deep, rich luster, completely free of scratches, chips, or swirl marks. The body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim pieces are intact and pristine. The interior is equally impressive, with no visible wear on the seats, carpets, or dashboard; every surface looks and feels nearly new. Mechanically, this car runs and drives exceptionally well \u2014 the engine starts immediately, idles smoothly, and delivers strong, responsive performance. All systems, including climate control, infotainment, lighting, and power accessories, function exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely rivals a new-car experience. Ideal for a buyer who demands the best and wants a car they can drive with complete confidence from day one.",
